<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<!-- Darya's Updates: added contents of the privacy policy -->
<p>We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>
<p>By using thiis application, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We may collect the following information when you use our application:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, NetId, and UTDId.</li>
    <li><strong>Review Data:</strong> Peer review scores you submit for your teammates.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>Your data is used to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Facilitate the submission of peer review scores.</li>
    <li>Calculate and display average scores for reviews you have received.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell or share your personal information to third parties. </p>
<p>Only authorized personnel have access to your data. Authorized personnel include UTD professors and administrators.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Access the average peer review scores you received, once they become available.</li>
    <li>Request corrections to any peer review submissions by contacting your professor.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact your professor.</p>
